    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 46rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
      The first edition ran in July 2022 at the Hertie Centre for International Security in Berlin.
      The second followed from 9 to 15 July 2023, welcoming 21 fully-funded participants who each
      received a €1,000 stipend towards travel and accommodation. Both were directed by Mauro Gilli
      (ETH Zurich), Marina Henke (Hertie School) and Hugo Meijer (Sciences Po). The Hertie School
      filmed each week, giving a sense of the lectures, the workshops, and the people who took part.
    </p>
